text.tspan: This represents the 0.25" recommended margin. All text, images,
logos, and the barcode must remain inside the margin.
Your background artwork must fill this area in order to ensure
that the printing consistently reaches the edge of the page. Do not
place logos, text, or essential images in the bleed area.
Please make sure to delete all cover template
guidelines and instructions bfore uploading your file.
